Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix;;81;;78;;PG-13;;Now in his fifth year at Hogwarts, Harry (Daniel Radcliffe) learns that many in the wizarding community do not know the truth of his encounter with Lord Voldemort. Cornelius Fudge, minister of Magic, appoints his toady, Dolores Umbridge, as Defense Against the Dark Arts teacher, for he fears that professor Dumbledore will take his job. But her teaching is deficient and her methods, cruel, so Harry prepares a group of students to defend the school against a rising tide of evil.;;Adventure,Fantasy;;David Yates;;2007;;Daniel Radcliffe,Rupert Grint,Emma Watson,Helena Bonham Carter,Robbie Coltrane,Michael Gambon,Gary Oldman,Imelda Staunton,Richard Griffiths,Jason Isaacs,Alan Rickman,Fiona Shaw,Maggie Smith,Timothy Spall,David Thewlis,Emma Thompson,Julie Walters,Harry Melling,Mark Williams;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/harry_potter_and_the_order_of_the_phoenix